      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of age and use. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor dings, and some fading in the clear coat on the roof and hood. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows significant wear and some staining, and a few plastic trim pieces are loose or cracked. Mechanically, the car starts and runs consistently, though the suspension is starting to feel soft and it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future. It is an honest car for someone looking for affordable transportation who doesn't mind a bit of character and some upcoming DIY projects.",
