      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 represents a superlative example of the high-revving S65 platform. Featuring a 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 equipped with individual throttle bodies, this unit delivers razor-sharp throttle response and linear power delivery up to its 8,400 RPM redline. The six-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a variable M differential lock to maximize lateral grip and exit speeds. This specimen is in impeccable condition, retaining its original factory finish and a pristine interior. Critical preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service, has been completed to ensure mechanical longevity. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and staggered Competition Package alloys, maintaining the precise turn-in and neutral handling balance that defines this iconic rear-drive longitudinal layout.",
      "price": 48500.0,
