      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, maintained with obsessive care to preserve its showroom integrity. The exterior boasts a flawless deep-gloss finish with zero swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections; it has been professionally ceramic-coated and garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment since day one. Inside, the cabin still carries that distinct new-car scent, featuring pristine leather upholstery without a single crease or bolster wear, complemented by high-definition displays and tactile controls that feel crisp and unused. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive, documented service history performed exclusively by certified master technicians using only OEM parts. Every button, sensor, and mechanical component functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Included in the sale are both original master keys, the complete set of factory manuals, and a custom-fitted premium car cover. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade specimen that satisfies the most discerning standards.",
